{"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/SignalGroupSignalName\/notify"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/SignalGroupSignalName"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"explicitNotify"},{"text":", then any call to ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If they did pass ","type":"text"},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when they e